        public MessageHistoryBuilder()
        Creates a new MessageHistoryBuilder, setting the following non-nullable fields:
        • EventName: a generated string
        • DestinationID: the id for the console message transport
        • Status: Acked
        • AckCount: 1
        • SendOrder: a generated integer
        • CreationTime: the current date and time
        • OrigMsgId: a generated number
